{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon, Original Serialized Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-07",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/maltesefalcon_2511_librivox/maltesefalcon_07_hammett.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "Chapter 7 - G in the Air",
  "reader_name": "Mark Nelson",
  "page_num": 6,
  "page_total": 7,
  "page_start_sec": 1233.216,
  "page_end_sec": 1476.22,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.735,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 1233.216,
      "end": 1235.56,
      "text": "Dundee clicked his teeth together and said through them,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1236.352,
      "end": 1237.12,
      "text": "\"'Let us in.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1237.984,
      "end": 1239.88,
      "text": "Spade's lip twitched over an eye-tooth.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1239.92,
      "end": 1240.58,
      "text": "He said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1241.408,
      "end": 1242.42,
      "text": "\"'You're not coming in.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1243.26,
      "end": 1244.46,
      "text": "What do you want to do about it?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1245.0,
      "end": 1245.7,
      "text": "Try to get in?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1246.4,
      "end": 1247.42,
      "text": "Or do your talking here?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1247.78,
      "end": 1249.216,
      "text": "or go to hell.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1250.32,
      "end": 1251.16,
      "text": "Tom groaned.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1251.58,
      "end": 1252.18,
      "text": "Dundee,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1252.3,
      "end": 1253.66,
      "text": "still speaking through his teeth,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1253.76,
      "end": 1253.98,
      "text": "said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1255.424,
      "end": 1257.32,
      "text": "\"'It'd pay you to play along with us a little,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1257.42,
      "end": 1257.74,
      "text": "Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 1258.528,
      "end": 1260.78,
      "text": "You've got away with this and you've got away with that,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1260.88,
      "end": 1262.59,
      "text": "but you can't keep it up forever.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1263.968,
      "end": 1267.24,
      "text": "\"'Stop me when you can,' Spade replied arrogantly.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1268.352,
      "end": 1269.48,
      "text": "\"'That's what I'll do.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1270.432,
      "end": 1271.74,
      "text": "Dundee put his hands behind him",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1271.84,
      "end": 1274.68,
      "text": "and thrust his hard face up toward the private detectives."
    },
    {
      "start": 1276.224,
      "end": 1277.88,
      "text": "There's talk going around that you and",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1277.88,
      "end": 1279.48,
      "text": "Archer's wife were cheating on him."
    },
    {
      "start": 1280.512,
      "end": 1281.28,
      "text": "Spade laughed.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1282.14,
      "end": 1284.2,
      "text": "That sounds like something you thought up yourself.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1285.7,
      "end": 1287.1,
      "text": "Then there's not anything to it?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1288.064,
      "end": 1288.68,
      "text": "Not anything.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1290.26,
      "end": 1290.82,
      "text": "The talk is,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1291.12,
      "end": 1291.88,
      "text": "Dundee said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1292.8,
      "end": 1294.66,
      "text": "that she tried to get a divorce out",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1294.66,
      "end": 1296.38,
      "text": "of him so she could put in with you,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1297.02,
      "end": 1298.2,
      "text": "but he wouldn't give it to her."
    },
    {
      "start": 1299.04,
      "end": 1299.8,
      "text": "Anything to that?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1300.66,
      "end": 1301.3,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1303.168,
      "end": 1305.98,
      "text": "\"'There's even talk,' Dundee continued stolidly,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1306.56,
      "end": 1308.34,
      "text": "\"'that that's why he was put on the spot.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1310.016,
      "end": 1311.64,
      "text": "Spade seemed mildly amused.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1312.64,
      "end": 1314.22,
      "text": "\"'Don't be a hog,' he said.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1314.82,
      "end": 1317.64,
      "text": "\"'You haven't tried to pin more than one murder at a time on me."
    },
    {
      "start": 1318.78,
      "end": 1320.22,
      "text": "Your first notion that I knocked",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1320.22,
      "end": 1322.02,
      "text": "Thursby off because he'd killed Miles"
    },
    {
      "start": 1322.28,
      "end": 1324.62,
      "text": "falls apart if you blame me for killing Miles,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1324.74,
      "end": 1325.28,
      "text": "too.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1326.6,
      "end": 1328.63,
      "text": "\"'You haven't heard me say you killed anybody,'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1329.376,
      "end": 1329.8,
      "text": "Dundee replied.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1330.66,
      "end": 1332.9,
      "text": "You're the one that's been bringing that up.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1333.56,
      "end": 1334.5,
      "text": "But suppose I did."
    },
    {
      "start": 1335.28,
      "end": 1336.0,
      "text": "You could have blipped",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1336.0,
      "end": 1336.42,
      "text": "them both."
    },
    {
      "start": 1337.696,
      "end": 1339.168,
      "text": "There's a way of figuring it.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1340.3,
      "end": 1340.66,
      "text": "Uh-huh.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1341.48,
      "end": 1343.5,
      "text": "I could have butchered Miles to get his wife,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1343.64,
      "end": 1345.18,
      "text": "and then Thursby so I could hang"
    },
    {
      "start": 1345.3,
      "end": 1346.44,
      "text": "Miles's murder on him."
    },
    {
      "start": 1347.712,
      "end": 1348.62,
      "text": "That's a swell system.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1348.84,
      "end": 1351.34,
      "text": "Or will be when I get around to killing somebody"
    },
    {
      "start": 1351.46,
      "end": 1353.74,
      "text": "else so I can accuse them of Thursby's murder."
    },
    {
      "start": 1354.39,
      "end": 1356.12,
      "text": "Am I supposed to keep that up?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1356.88,
      "end": 1357.2,
      "text": "What are you",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1357.3,
      "end": 1357.66,
      "text": "gonna do,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1357.88,
      "end": 1361.26,
      "text": "charge me with all the killings in San Francisco from now on?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1362.3,
      "end": 1362.8,
      "text": "Tom said.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1363.5,
      "end": 1363.66,
      "text": "\"'Aw,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1363.76,
      "end": 1364.54,
      "text": "cut the comedy,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1364.66,
      "end": 1364.9,
      "text": "Sam."
    },
    {
      "start": 1366.0,
      "end": 1368.0,
      "text": "You know damn well we don't like this any"
    },
    {
      "start": 1368.0,
      "end": 1368.78,
      "text": "more than you do,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1368.94,
      "end": 1370.74,
      "text": "but we got to do our work."
    },
    {
      "start": 1372.06,
      "end": 1373.08,
      "text": "I hope you've got something",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1373.08,
      "end": 1376.52,
      "text": "to do besides pop in here early every morning asking me a lot of damn"
    },
    {
      "start": 1376.6,
      "end": 1377.62,
      "text": "fool questions.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1378.64,
      "end": 1381.96,
      "text": "\"'And getting damn lying answers,' Dundee added deliberately.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1383.36,
      "end": 1385.48,
      "text": "\"'Easy now,' Spade cautioned him.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1386.752,
      "end": 1389.54,
      "text": "Dundee looked up and down and then looked him straight in the eyes.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1390.98,
      "end": 1392.52,
      "text": "\"'If you say there was nothing between",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1392.52,
      "end": 1394.84,
      "text": "you and Archer's wife,' Dundee said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1395.552,
      "end": 1396.12,
      "text": "\"'you're a liar,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1396.46,
      "end": 1397.72,
      "text": "and I'm telling you so.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1398.34,
      "end": 1401.46,
      "text": "A startled look came into Tom's small eyes."
    },
    {
      "start": 1402.336,
      "end": 1404.24,
      "text": "Spade moistened his lips with the tip of his",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1404.34,
      "end": 1404.98,
      "text": "tongue and asked,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1405.35,
      "end": 1407.72,
      "text": "\"'Is that the hot tip that brought you"
    },
    {
      "start": 1407.72,
      "end": 1409.86,
      "text": "here at this ungodly time of night?'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1410.976,
      "end": 1411.86,
      "text": "\"'That's one of them.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1412.832,
      "end": 1413.48,
      "text": "\"'And the others?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1414.14,
      "end": 1416.58,
      "text": "Dundee drew down the corners of his mouth."
    },
    {
      "start": 1417.728,
      "end": 1418.46,
      "text": "Let us in.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1419.072,
      "end": 1422.78,
      "text": "He nodded significantly at the doorway in which Spade stood."
    },
    {
      "start": 1424.032,
      "end": 1425.48,
      "text": "Spade frowned and shook his head.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1426.624,
      "end": 1428.28,
      "text": "Dundee's mouth corners lifted a little",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1428.28,
      "end": 1429.96,
      "text": "in a smile of grim satisfaction."
    },
    {
      "start": 1431.7,
      "end": 1433.22,
      "text": "There must have been something in it,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1433.72,
      "end": 1434.42,
      "text": "he told Tom."
    },
    {
      "start": 1435.648,
      "end": 1436.88,
      "text": "Tom shifted his feet,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1437.0,
      "end": 1438.26,
      "text": "and not looking at either man,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1438.34,
      "end": 1438.7,
      "text": "mumbled,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1439.552,
      "end": 1440.04,
      "text": "God knows.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1440.36,
      "end": 1442.98,
      "text": "\"'What's this?' Spade asked."
    },
    {
      "start": 1443.1,
      "end": 1444.06,
      "text": "\"'Charades?'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1445.376,
      "end": 1445.8,
      "text": "\"'All right,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1445.8,
      "end": 1446.22,
      "text": "Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 1446.32,
      "end": 1447.2,
      "text": "We're going.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1448.064,
      "end": 1449.34,
      "text": "Dundee buttoned up his overcoat.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1450.68,
      "end": 1452.14,
      "text": "\"'We'll be in to see you now and then.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1452.46,
      "end": 1454.62,
      "text": "Maybe you're right in bucking us."
    },
    {
      "start": 1455.12,
      "end": 1455.64,
      "text": "Think it over.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1457.152,
      "end": 1458.66,
      "text": "\"'Uh-huh,' Spade said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1458.8,
      "end": 1459.24,
      "text": "grinning."
    },
    {
      "start": 1460.192,
      "end": 1461.36,
      "text": "\"'Glad to see you any time,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1461.42,
      "end": 1461.62,
      "text": "Lieutenant."
    },
    {
      "start": 1461.96,
      "end": 1463.56,
      "text": "And whenever I'm not busy,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1463.72,
      "end": 1464.832,
      "text": "I'll let you in.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1465.61,
      "end": 1467.88,
      "text": "A voice in Spade's living room screamed,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1468.26,
      "end": 1468.26,
      "text": "word."
    },
    {
      "start": 1468.34,
      "end": 1468.96,
      "text": "Help!"
    },
    {
      "start": 1469.3,
      "end": 1469.78,
      "text": "Help!"
    },
    {
      "start": 1470.12,
      "end": 1470.54,
      "text": "Police!"
    },
    {
      "start": 1471.02,
      "end": 1471.904,
      "text": "Help!\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1473.06,
      "end": 1473.42,
      "text": "The voice,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1473.66,
      "end": 1475.14,
      "text": "high and thin and shrill,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1475.16,
      "end": 1475.4,
      "text": "was"
    },
    {
      "start": 1475.44,
      "end": 1476.22,
      "text": "Joel Cairo's."
    }
  ]
}